gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 142, Jazz 121
gameRecap.excerpt: Denver defeats Utah, 142-121. For Denver, Jamal Murray ties a season-high with 37 points (six 3PM), seven assists, and two steals with Nikola Jokic recording 26 points, six rebounds, eight assists, and two blocks to lead the way in the victory. Keyonte George finished with 29 points (five 3PM), five rebounds, and six assists while Jordan Clarkson tallied 22 points, four rebounds, and three steals for Utah in the losing effort. Denver improves to 44-20, while Utah moves to 28-36 in the loss.
